#: edx_exams/apps/core/templates/email/proctoring_attempt_rejected.html:12
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Your proctored exam \"%(exam_name)s\" in\n"
"        <a href=\"%(course_url)s\">%(course_url)s</a> was reviewed and the\n"
"        course team has identified one or more violations of the proctored exam rules. Examples\n"
"        of issues that may result in a rules violation include browsing\n"
"        the internet, using a phone,\n"
"        or getting help from another person. As a result of the identified issue(s),\n"
"        you did not successfully meet the proctored exam requirements.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        您的监考考试 \"%(exam_name)s\" 在\n"
"        <a href=\"%(course_url)s\">%(course_url)s</a> 已经审核，课程团队已发现一个或多个违反监考考试规则的行为。浏览互联网、使用手机或寻求他人帮助等行为可能会被视为违规。由于存在上述问题，您未能满足监考考试要求。\n"
"    "

#: edx_exams/apps/core/templates/email/proctoring_attempt_rejected.html:25
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"        To appeal your proctored exam results, please reach out with any relevant information\n"
"        about your exam at \n"
"        <a href=\"%(contact_url)s\">\n"
"            %(contact_url_text)s\n"
"        </a>.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        若要对您的监考考试成绩提出申诉，请提供与考试相关的任何信息，并通过\n"
"        <a href=\"%(contact_url)s\">\n"
"            %(contact_url_text)s\n"
"        </a>与我们联系。\n"
"    "

#: edx_exams/apps/core/templates/email/proctoring_attempt_submitted.html:12
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Your proctored exam \"%(exam_name)s\" in\n"
"        <a href=\"%(course_url)s\">%(course_url)s</a> was submitted\n"
"        successfully and will now be reviewed to ensure all exam\n"
"        rules were followed. You should receive an email with your exam\n"
"        status within 5 business days.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        您的监考考试 \"%(exam_name)s\" 在\n"
"        <a href=\"%(course_url)s\">%(course_url)s</a> 已成功提交，现正进入审核阶段以确保所有考试规则均得到遵守。您将在5个工作日内收到包含考试状态信息的邮件。\n"
"    "

#: edx_exams/apps/core/templates/email/proctoring_attempt_verified.html:12
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Your proctored exam \"%(exam_name)s\" in\n"
"        <a href=\"%(course_url)s\">%(course_url)s</a> was reviewed and you\n"
"        met all proctoring requirements.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        您的监考考试 \"%(exam_name)s\" 在\n"
"        <a href=\"%(course_url)s\">%(course_url)s</a> 的审核结果显示，您已满足所有监考要求。\n"
"    "

#: edx_exams/apps/core/templates/email/proctoring_attempt_verified.html:21
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"    If you have any questions about your results, you can reach out at \n"
"        <a href=\"%(contact_url)s\">\n"
"            %(contact_url_text)s\n"
"        </a>.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    如果您对结果有任何疑问，您可以通过\n"
"        <a href=\"%(contact_url)s\">\n"
"            %(contact_url_text)s\n"
"        </a>与我们取得联系。\n"
"    "
